---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Fernando Delgado - Product Leader | 5x Founder | Former Google, YouTube, Yahoo" bodyClass="collection-type-page homepage">

  <!-- Full-width banner photo at 50% aspect ratio (original image: 7740x3870) -->
  <div class="sqs-block image-block">
    <div class="image-block-outer-wrapper">
      <figure class="sqs-block-image-figure intrinsic">
        <div class="image-block-wrapper">
          <div style="height:350px;overflow:hidden;border-radius:8px;">
            <img
              src="/images/fernando-delgado.jpg"
              alt=""
              loading="eager"
              width="7740"
              height="3870"
              style="display:block;object-fit:cover;width:100%;height:100%;object-position:50% 50%;"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <figcaption class="image-caption-wrapper">
          <div class="image-caption"><p>Fernando Delgado - Product Executive  | 5x Founder | Ex-Google, YouTube, Yahoo | Lifelong Learner</p></div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bio text -->
  <div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html">
    <div class="sqs-block-content">
      <div class="sqs-html-content">
        <p>Fernando Delgado builds world-class products that blend purpose, simplicity, and global scale. With two decades of experience launching and growing technology products, he brings a rare mix of entrepreneurial drive and corporate leadership.</p>

        <p>Fernando is a seasoned product leader and 5x founder with a track record of building and scaling technology that impacts billions. Over the past 16+ years, he's led high-impact teams at Google, YouTube, Microsoft, and Yahoo, shipping products used daily around the globe.</p>

        <p>At Google, Fernando co-led the development of Backup by Google One, now integrated into more than 2 billion Android devices. This effort helped scale Google's mobile storage business from $50M to over $1B ARR through deep integrations with Photos, Gmail, Drive, and Android.</p>

        <p>At YouTube, he shaped the strategy for YouTube Courses, a structured learning product designed to support creator-led education.</p>

        <p>At Yahoo, Fernando led mobile product for Yahoo Mail and the homepage app, growing the mobile user base to 50M+ monthly active users. He also founded Yahoo's Associate Product Manager program, mentoring over 23 future product leaders now at companies like Stripe, Waymo, Apple, and Uber.</p>

        <p>Fernando's entrepreneurial path started in 2012. He's founded 5 ventures, each focused on combining agility with the highest standards. Most recently, he co-founded Techito, which became Colorado's #1 rated short-term rental Super Host.</p>

        <p>Based in Barcelona, Fernando blends Silicon Valley product rigor with a founder's adaptability and vision. A lifelong learner with a deep commitment to personal growth, he's always looking for ways to use his skills to do good.</p>

        <p>Fernando is an active volunteer with <a href="https://www.bemyeyes.com" target="_blank">Be My Eyes</a>.</p>

        <p>If you're interested in getting in touch, please send a note to <a href="mailto:hello@fernandodelgado.com"><strong>hello@fernandodelgado.com</strong></a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
